{"tid":2197574,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(抒發下) 睇到依家既廣州人 就會見到將來既香港","createTime":"2020-09-10T16:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T07:02:50.000Z","uid":53440,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"148b938a97ed42edc299e49a51d0ab84e2109277","tid":2197574,"uid":53440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:55:35.000Z","msg":"無意中睇到youtube有個頻道係講廣州人唔識講廣東話<br />\n有興趣睇可以飛去34秒嗰度睇 大陸人整所以殘體字<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dL2FZChaBJQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdL2FZChaBJQ&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FJnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=c7546d85\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dL2FZChaBJQ</a><br />\n<br />\n其實依家香港都做緊相同嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我出咗嚟社會唔太清楚 但係依家已經實行咗普教小普教中<br />\n喺街有時候都聽到啲小朋友係講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋10幾歲有獨立思想既埋下守護香港嘅根喺個心底<br />\n但係面對住將來嗰班 由細教到大既普通話人<br />\n都唔知到時會唔會批鬥反我哋粵語撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一諗到香港變成咁樣就好可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n純粹抒發下 都唔知有啲咩可以做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60d08a482a2518f6aa7ae0c11101ea7c4e7bc5c","tid":2197574,"uid":14494,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T17:13:03.000Z","msg":"睇蒙古東突就知, 廣東話遲早會比國話取代<br />\n但始終仲係香港, 希望到時你會用英文做母語教仔女"},{"pid":"186460d99b2bff85e2e3722bea2c6bfd2d09638b","tid":2197574,"uid":53440,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a60d08a482a2518f6aa7ae0c11101ea7c4e7bc5c","tid":2197574,"uid":14494,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T17:13:03.000Z","msg":"睇蒙古東突就知, 廣東話遲早會比國話取代<br />\n但始終仲係香港, 希望到時你會用英文做母語教仔女"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T17:19:33.000Z","msg":"香港只要一日係中共揸旗 一定冇運行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4035d0766e128ea00454ed